reviewText: I'll bet money this DVD is a VHS/or BETA recording that was converted to DVD! Picture and sound quality is TERRIBLE! I guess for a few bucks it's not bad but I expected better!!!
This is a digital version of a great race that I once recorded highlights of on a VHS tape but I wanted the video on a disc.  Packaging also looks nice.
This is when stock car racing was good racing. Any sports fan would enjoy Nascar back then. A must buy for all race fans.
